9213.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends north, south, and west.
A path follows a stream to the east.

9256.name: Floating in Air
description: You look down and see the ground 100 feet below you.  The wind whispering
in your ear seems to reassure you that this is fine.  To the north aways
you spy a portal of sorts.  To the west is more thin air.

9216.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The Canyon floor extends north, south and west.

9234.name: Elemental Bay
description: The water is crystal clear here and you can see the bottom of the bay 30 feet
below you.  Then you realize you are walking on the water itself.  Truly
magical water indeed.  Though you splash through the bay you do not get wet.

9253.name: Mesa West
description: An electric path starts to the west.  The mesa continues to the east.
Or you can climb down to the canyon floor to the south.

9214.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about. The canyon floor extends north, east, and south.
To the west a garden is on fire.

9238.name: Fiery Pathway
description: You tread carefully along a path which dips and turns among pits of fire and
beds of coals.  A garden to the west glows with an everlasting fire.

9225.name: Darkest Caves
description: Your light doesn't even seem to work here.  Even magical light sources seem
only to illuminate about a foot ahead of you.  You suddenly realize that the
path has descended quite a bit but you didn't notice before because of the
darkness.  You sense a great presence off to the east aways.

9208.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at all.
In general, it is calm, yet there is always a incessant buzz of things
going on about.  The canyon continues north and east.

9252.name: Lightning Chamber
description: There is some sort of control panel here. Apparently the Lightning Ruler
observes and controls electric forces from here.  A set of steps carved into
the hill lead down to a causeway.

9259.name: Windy Tunnel
description: A tunnel leads east.  To the west you can enter a portal. The wind in
this tunnel is quite fierce, it seems as if it's forced.
Through the portal you see nothing but sky.

9202.name: Mountain Path
description: You are on a rocky mountain path leading up and around a steep mountainside.
You sense a glow from the area beyond the mountain, which you cannot see yet.

9222.name: Darker Caves
description: You can barely see your way even with a light source.  The rocks of the cave
are even darker than the darkness.  You hear a powerful humming all around
you.  Cave paths go south and west roughly; it's hard to tell exactly when you
can't see where you are going.

9227.name: Earth Chamber
description: This is the abode of the Earth Ruler.  He decides about earthquakes,
landslides, and avalanches.  The Earth Ruler sits upon a huge marble throne
carved into the wall.
The ruler notices your stare, and doesn't like it one bit!  The whole
earth seems to shake with his emotion.

9246.name: Electric Pathway
description: The pathway glows and hums because of the electricity pulsing through it.
It seems almost soothing to your weary feet.  To the north there is a
sunken-in area.  A path leads east also.

9209.name: Elemental Gateway
description: To the west a path dips and winds among some flowing firepits.  To the
northeast a path goes toward the river.  Beyond toward the northeast and
northwest are outcrops which rise up from the canyon floor. To the east there
is a cave mouth which leads into the canyon wall.  And to the south the path
leads up, away, and out of the canyon.  Various pure and cross-breeds of
elemental forms wander the canyon floor, which extends in a wide swath
northwards.

9255.name: Floating in Air
description: Last you knew, you were walking on the mesa.  Abruptly the path dropped
from beneath your feet much to quick for you to recover.  Instead of
plunging to your death, you seemingly miss the ground and begin walking
on air.  The space to the north and east seems just thin air, but you can
walk there.  The pathway you came from is to the south.

9230.name: Elemental Bay
description: The water is crystal clear here and you can see the bottom of the bay 30 feet
below you.  Then you realize you are walking on the water itself.  Truly
magical water indeed.  Though you splash through the bay you do not get wet.

9204.name: Blind Curve on the Mountain Path
description: This looks like a normal mountain path, but it is NOT!  This section of the
path is habitated by a huge (and of course, man-eating) Cyclops.  The path
makes its final ascent to an overlook.

9217.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about. The canyon floor extends east and south.  You can
climb a rise in the canyon floor to the north.

9218.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends east, south, and west.

9206.name: Overlook
description: You see various elemental servants wandering around the canyon.  The noise of
humming coming from the canyon gets louder.  The path makes a steep descent
into the canyon here.

9242.name: Burning Gardens
description: Everywhere around you the landscape is afire; the rocks, the shrubs and even
the air seems to be aflame.  Curiously, the magical fire does not seem to
consume its hosts.  A path leads east among some fire pits.

9245.name: Fire Chamber
description: The fire ruler sits upon a throne made of blue flame.  Little flickers of
flame dance to and fro for the entertainment of the ruler.

9220.name: Dark Cave
description: You notice a path winding east among some huge boulders.  You feel a powerful
source of energy from that direction.

9237.name: Fiery Pathway
description: You tread carefully along a path which dips and turns among geysers of fire.
Miniature volcanoes spew lava in rivers.  The fire is hot but not altogether
dangerous.  The path extends east and south.

9203.name: Mountainside Tombs
description: There are a few stone heaps here and there, the tombs of those who did not
last the arduous journey up the mountain.  Curiously you notice a few
uncovered bodies which don't seem to have died of exhaustion.  The path curves
east around the mountain.
You are sure glad that YOU aren't under one of those piles!
Many of the tombstones have the same name on them, 'Raff'.  He must come
here a lot.
They look as if their necks have been broken and their flesh, chewed.

9221.name: Darker Caves
description: You can barely see your way even with a light source.  The rocks of the cave
are even darker than the darkness.  You hear a powerful humming all around
you.  Cave paths go south and east roughly, its hard to tell exactly when you
can't see where you are going.

9224.name: Darker Caves
description: You can barely see your way even with a light source.  The rocks of the cave
are even darker than the darkness.  You hear a powerful humming all around you.
Cave paths go north, south and west roughly, it's hard to tell exactly when you
can't see where you are going.

9210.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always a incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends north and west.  There is a
cave mouth set into the canyon wall to the east.

9201.name: Mountain Path
description: You are on a mountain path which ascends a steep mountainside.  The trail
curves around the mountain so that you cannot really see what lies ahead.
You do sense great power though coming from the area behind the mountain.

9257.name: Floating in Air
description: You look down and see the ground 100 feet below you.  The wind whispering
in your ear seems to reassure you that this is fine.  To the east aways
you spy a portal of sorts.  To the south is more thin air.

9219.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends south and west.  You can
climb a rise in the canyon floor to the north.

9223.name: Darker Caves
description: You can barely see your way even with a light source.  The rocks of the cave
are even darker than the darkness.  You hear a powerful humming all around you.
Cave paths go north, south and east roughly; it's hard to tell exactly when
you can't see where you are going.

9251.name: Lightning Causeway
description: Up a set of stairs carved into the hill you see intermittent flashes of
lightning.  A continuous hum also comes form that direction.  To the west
is the electric playground.

9236.name: Water Chamber
description: This chamber was magically created here on the floor of the bay.  It looks
like it's been here for a long, long time.  Though you are 'under water' there
is no difficulty breathing normally, and oddly you do not feel the pressure of
the water above you.

9235.name: Elemental Bay
description: The water is crystal clear here and you can see the bottom of the bay 30 feet
below you.  Then you realize you are walking on the water itself.  Truly
magical water indeed.  Though you splash through the bay you do not get wet.

9249.name: Electric Playground
description: Though there is a seemingly carefree atmosphere here, you sense that
something much more important takes place near by.  The playground continues
south and east.

9250.name: Electric Playground
description: Though there is a seemingly carefree atmosphere here, you sense that
something much more important takes place near by.  The playground is
south and west.  Something more important catches your eye to the east.

9258.name: Floating in Air
description: You look down and see the ground 100 feet below you.  The wind whispering
in your ear seems to reassure you that this is fine. There is a portal
hanging in midair here. It is to the east.  You can float south or west
if you'd like.
Through the portal you see a tunnel.

9229.name: In the River
description: To continue you had to walk right in the river.  Though you walk along in
water up to your knees, you do not seem to get wet.  A bay stretches out to
the north and the river goes south.

9212.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends in all directions.

9231.name: Elemental Bay
description: The water is crystal clear here and you can see the bottom of the bay 30 feet
below you.  Then you realize you are walking on the water itself.  Truly
magical water indeed.  Though you splash through the bay you do not get wet.

9247.name: Electric Playground
description: Though there is a seemingly carefree atmosphere here, you sense that
something much more important takes place near by.  The electric playground
extends north and east.

9233.name: Elemental Bay
description: The water is crystal clear here and you can see the bottom of the bay 30 feet
below you.  Then you realize you are walking on the water itself.  Truly
magical water indeed.  Though you splash through the bay you do not get wet.

9239.name: {yEn{Ytran{yce {*to {RC{Bo{Gs{Rm{Bo {YCa{yny{Yon{x
description: On the other side of the bay, the rock walls of the Elemental
Canyon open up to reveal another canyon running to the east.  Either
side of the tall rock walls almost touch in this opening, above has
been carved into an archway.  Cosmo Canyon is the words carved into
the stone.

9226.name: Darkest Caves
description: Your light doesn't even seem to work here.  Even magical light sources seem
only to illuminate about a foot ahead of you.  You suddenly realize that the
path has descended quite a bit but you didn't notice before because of the
darkness.  You sense a great presence directly to the east.

9248.name: Electric Playground
description: Though there is a seemingly carefree atmosphere here, you sense that
something much more important takes place near by.  There is an electric
path heading away south.  The playground extends north and west.

9254.name: Mesa East
description: A path starts to the north.  The mesa continues to the west.
Or you can climb down to the canyon floor to the south.

9228.name: By the River
description: The water in the river seems to bubble and froth with magic.  Though it
splashes playfully on you, it does not seem wet.  The path leads north closer
to the water. To the west you see a T-intersection.

9232.name: Elemental Bay
description: The water is crystal clear here and you can see the bottom of the bay 30 feet
below you.  Then you realize you are walking on the water itself.  Truly
magical water indeed.  Though you splash through the bay you do not get wet.

9215.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends in all directions.

9205.name: Vista
description: This is a stunning vista overlooking a canyon.  There is a sign here that says:
BEHOLD -- ELEMENTAL CANYON
Fire leaps up from firepits in the western part of the canyon.  The sky looks
funny, and the air seems hazy to the northwest.  Electricity sparks
intermittently in the northeast.  To the east you see a strong, magic-looking
river flowing through the canyon.  Also to the east you spy a cave entrance
leading into the canyon wall.  The path descends to the north to another
overlook.

9211.name: Floor of the Canyon
description: Various elemental forms wander the floor of the canyon.  Some seem to be
going about their business, while others seem to have no business at
all.  In general, it is calm, yet there is always an incessant buzz of
things going on about.  The canyon floor extends off to the north, east,
and south.

9207.name: Entrance to Elemental Canyon
description: You are awed by the sounds and sights of great powers at works here.
Elemental servants bustle back and forth doing the biddings of the elemental
rulers.  You see a sort of cross roads to the north, and you can climb up to
the overlook here.

9216.name: a small snowflake~
description: It looks a little blue.
9216.keywords: oldstyle snowflake snow flake ice elemental~

9217.name: a small rock~
description: It seems to be a small living pebble!
9217.keywords: oldstyle pebble rock earth stone elemental~

9218.name: a small spark~
description: Zipping from place to place at the speed of light is tough work.
9218.room_name: A small spark of electricity fizzles here.

9219.name: a small blob of acid~
description: The magical blob of acid is a cross between lightning and water.
9219.room_name: A small blob of acid aimlessly eats away at the stone.

9220.name: a lava beast~
description: The magical lava beast is a cross between fire and earth.
9220.room_name: A lava beast spews from place to place.

9221.name: a mud monster~
description: The magical mud monster is a cross between water and earth.

9222.name: an elemental mist~
description: The magical mist is a cross between water and air.
9222.room_name: The air is magically misty here.

9223.name: a particle~
description: The magical manifestation of energy.
9223.room_name: A sub-atomic particle is too small for you to see.

9224.name: a dust cloud~
description: The magical dust cloud is a cross between air and earth.
9224.room_name: A dust cloud blowing by makes you sneeze.

9225.name: an eddie~
description: The magical eddie current is a manifestation of an air elemental.
9225.room_name: A small eddie current swirls junk around here.

9226.name: the Blue Flame~
description:
As you look you see what seems to be a face and almost a 
humanoid figure somehow trapped in the fire.
9226.room_name: The Blue Flame burns mysteriously here.

9227.name: the Magneto~
description: A humanoid figure seems to be trapped in the field of the Magneto.
9227.room_name: The Magneto considers zapping you for the heck of it.

9228.name: the Ice Bandit~
description: A humanoid figure encased in ice but still apparently alive.
9228.room_name: The Ice Bandit strikes cold fear in your heart.

9229.name: the Rock Monster~
description: A humanoid figure trapped in stone seems alive.
9229.room_name: The Rock Monster considers you in stoney silence.

9230.name: the Hurricane~
description: A humanoid figure is trapped in the rushing wind.
9230.room_name: A Hurricane rages across the sky.

9231.name: an elemental magician~
description:
The elemental magician has come here in search of the fabled
Stone of Surrender which can be used to render opponents senseless.
9231.room_name: An elemental magician seeks magical stones for a spell.

9232.name: a rainbow warrior~
description:
The Rainbow Cult has received special powers for their service to 
the elemental forces.
9232.room_name: A warrior of the Rainbow Cult swears his loyalty.

9233.name: an illusionist~
description:
He seeks their aid for a powerful new spell of deception.

<wielded>            The Sword of Illusions
9233.room_name: The illusionist seeks the aid of the elemental forces.

9234.name: an alchemist~
description: Rare herbs are rumored to grow only in the canyon.
9234.room_name: An alchemist wanders by in search of magical herbs.

9235.name: a baby rainbow dragon~
description: It's only a baby by dragon standards.
9235.room_name: A baby rainbow dragon plays among the elements here.

9236.name: a little imp~
description: The little bugger steals stuff and is generally obnoxious.
9236.room_name: A little imp runs along being annoying.

9237.name: a HUGE elemental~
description: HUGE, need i say more?
9237.room_name: A HUGE elemental form stands here.

9238.name: the elixir vendor~
description: I WOULD NOT suggest you attack me ...!
9238.room_name: A vendor is willing to sell you elixirs.

9239.name: The {RC{Bo{Gs{Rm{Bo {YCa{yny{Yon{x Guard~
description: He looks like he's about to have dinner (maybe it's you?).
9239.room_name: A Guard of {RC{Bo{Gs{Rm{Bo {YCa{yny{Yon{x stands here, keeping watch.

9201.name: the mountain climber~
description: He wants to see what's on the other side of the mountain too.
9201.room_name: A mountain climber is making the same trek that you are.

9202.name: the cyclops~
description: He looks like he's about to have dinner (maybe it's you?).
9202.room_name: A hungry cyclops snarls at you!

9203.name: a tiny elemental~
description: Rather small for an elemental form, looks like a reject.
9203.room_name: A tiny elemental form wanders about.

9204.name: the elemental guardian~
description: You can't tell which kind of elemental it is, maybe it's a bit o' all of them?
9204.room_name: The elemental guardian of the canyon.

9205.name: a small elemental~
description: A small elemental, a resident of the canyon.

9206.name: a medium elemental~
description: A medium elemental, a resident of the canyon.

9208.name: the Earth Ruler~
description:
He looks as old as the earth itself.  He seems to know all the 
secrets and knowledge of the Earth.  You can't really tell where 
he begins and the rock wall ends.
9208.room_name: The Ruler of the earth elementals.

9209.name: the Fire Ruler~
description: As you look at him he seems to blend in with the fire in his throne.
9209.room_name: The Ruler of the fire elementals.

9210.name: The Air Ruler~
description: As you peer at him you seem to be looking at the sky itself.
9210.room_name: The Ruler of the air elementals.

9211.name: The Lightning Ruler~
description:
As you examine him there is a blinding flash of light and a deafening boom!
You rub your eyes and look and the ruler is there grinning at you.
9211.room_name: The Ruler of the lightning elementals.

9212.name: The Water Ruler~
description:
As you look at him he changes to mist, which swirls around you.  Just
as you get scared, it reforms in elemental form.
9212.room_name: The Ruler of the water elementals.

9214.name: a puddle~
description: It trickles along the ground and gets your feet wet.
9214.room_name: A small puddle of water elemental.

9215.name: a flame~
description: It smolders along the grass aimlessly.
